Package: knox
Architecture: all
Depends: bigtop-utils (>= 0.7), adduser
Description: The Apache Knox Gateway is an Application Gateway for interacting with the REST APIs and UIs
             of Apache Hadoop deployments.
             The Knox Gateway provides a single access point for all REST and HTTP interactions with Apache Hadoop
             clusters.